# Code Conventions

## Patterns

- Functional React components; state in `App.tsx`, pure helpers in modules
- Path alias: `@/` → `src/`
- Prefer extending existing abstractions (`PersistenceAdapter`, `RdsStore`, `LevelStatsDisplay`) over parallel implementations

## Testing

- Vitest; colocated `*.test.ts` next to modules
- Test behavior and pure logic, not React implementation details
- High priority: `score-frame`, `store`, `session-state`, `level-stats`, level catalog

## Persistence (current)

- Key: `rds-tracker-data` in `localStorage`
- `AppData`: `{ currentLevel, frames[], racks[] }`
- `submitFrame()` writes 1 frame + 3 racks atomically via adapter

## Changes

- Minimize diff scope; match existing naming and file layout
- Do not commit or deploy unless asked
- Level content sourced from BU Exam IV PDF; diagram logic in `rack-layouts.ts` + `RackDiagram.tsx`
